            <h5 class="card-title">Steven Pinker</h5>
            <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-body-secondary">Domain: Cognitive Psychology, Psycholinguistics</h6>
            <p class="card-text">Known for his research on language and the human mind. Pinker has written several influential books, including "The Language Instinct" and "How the Mind Works," exploring how language evolves and the cognitive processes behind it.</p>
